data(CoreGSM.GsmMode) - Method in class de.inovex.android.test.zomby.core.CoreGSM
allows you to change the state of your GPRS connection
valid values for mode are the following:
CoreGSM.GsmMode.UNREGISTERED, CoreGSM.GsmMode.HOME, CoreGSM.GsmMode.ROAMING, CoreGSM.GsmMode.SEARCHING, CoreGSM.GsmMode.DENIED, CoreGSM.GsmMode.OFF, CoreGSM.GsmMode.ON
IMPORTANT: the use from unregistered, searching, denied, off can disconnect the adb connection!!!
